title: Organic Corner Food Store and Bistro
description: As of Feb 2013, Poland's first combination organic food store and cafe (99% vegan menu). Uses super foods such as spirulina, chlorella, chia seeds, hemp seeds, goji berries and more. Also has some raw specialties in desserts, soups, power shakes and more. Has a kid's corner and cable tv. Speaks English, Polish, Italian and German. Wi-fi.
